1. Create a new Replit Node.js project


2. Upload repo or connect via GitHub


3. Set environment variables:

FIREBASE_API_KEY=...
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=...
BUZZ_MODE=production


4. Click Run ‚Üí it launches the same build used for Firebase Hosting.




